            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Target one creature within 10 spaces. They are invisible but still make sounds. This gives them advantage on stealth checks if they are wearing metal armor, or +5 on stealth checks if they are not wearing armor. If they make a melee attack, they may make a stealth vs. agility attack instead of their normal attack. Roll a d4 at the start of every round, if you roll a 1, the spell ends.",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Enhance: Increase the size of the die to see if the spell ends by 1, to a maximum of d12",
                "marks": [],
                "data": {}
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "nodeType": "paragraph",
            "data": {},
            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Enhance: Double the number of targets included in the spell",
